uantum observables and noisy post-selections is also\ndiscussed here. Our method can easily be generalized to the multi-partite\nsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Jul 2021 16:11:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 May 2022 05:58:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-06"}
