ectively under the similar FLOPs setting. By further\npretraining on the larger dataset ImageNet-21K, we achieve 87.5% Top-1 accuracy\non ImageNet-1K and high segmentation performance on ADE20K with 55.7 mIoU. The\ncode and models are available at\nhttps://github.com/microsoft/CSWin-Transformer.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Jul 2021 17:59:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Jul 2021 17:59:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 9 Jan 2022 05:49:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-11"}
