The\nmodel has two known limits: For infinite trap stiffness, it can be mapped to\ndiffusion in a tilted periodic potential. For infinite bath friction, the\noriginal Prandtl Tomlinson model is recovered. We find that the flow curve of\nthe model (roughly) crosses over between these two limiting cases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Jul 2021 10:33:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-13"}
